    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
