      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering prowess, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine exhibits exceptional compression across all cylinders, with the high-pressure double VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring surgical precision during corner exit. This specimen is mechanically pristine: the rear subframe has been preemptively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term structural and rotational integrity. The chassis retains its factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity, providing the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance synonymous with this platform. Finished in a deep gloss with a flawless cabin, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Garage kept. Clean title in hand. Inspection ready.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The factory paint retains its original deep luster with zero swirl marks or rock chips, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the leather remains supple and still carries that distinct new-car aroma, with every electronic component functioning exactly as it did on the showroom floor. Mechanically, it is flawless; I have a comprehensive binder of every service performed by certified technicians. With no track time, no accidents, and a spotless history, this is the finest example of this model currently on the market. It drives tight, shifts smoothly, and demands attention at every stop.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
